<br>
-Wessig: the Reset magi of this deck. If you happen to come across a Ritual Spear or two put them in and save them for wessig. <br>
<br>
-Hok: His power works well in all KT decks, preventing creature discard at most times.<br>
<br>
Combos-<br>
Agrilla/Agrilla/Agrilla: exchange fear to each of them so all 3 can attack twice.<br>
<br>
Agrilla/Baldar-Kill two creatures thet have less energy than Baldar with Fear.<br>
<br>
Alpine Xamf/Climbing Staff: More extra energy.<br>
<br>
Conclusion-<br>
Well I&#39;m not going to tell you how to play this deck step by step because you(the Beginner) should try it on your own experience (experiance is everything). But here is a suggestion- try Playing a strong wall of creatures and then play focus to gain a mega load of energy.<br>
<br>
Thats all! <br>
